    "user_title": "Create reactive Python notebooks with marimo",
    "value_statement": "Marimo is a reactive Python notebook environment that guarantees consistent state between code and outputs. This skill provides expert guidance for building interactive data apps and reproducible notebooks that run as scripts and deploy as web apps.",
